<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.4.6">
<l>paṇṭēṉa māyulakai yaṉṟiṭanta paṇpāḷā veṉṟu niṉṟu</l>
<l>toṇṭāṉēṉ tiruvaṭiyē tuṇaiyallāl tuṇaiyillēṉ collu kiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>vaṇṭēntum malarppuṟavil vaṇcēṟai yemperumā ṉaṭiyār tammai</l>
<l>kaṇṭēṉuk kitukāṇī reṉneñcuṅ kaṇṇiṇaiyuṅ kaḷikku māṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Always saying, “You of [fine] qualities who once long ago dug up the earth</l>
<l rend="indent">dug up the earth as a boar,”</l>
<l>I, who am your servant, have no help without the help of your divine feet,</l>
<l rend="indent">of your divine feet, I am telling [you].</l>
<l>See, for me who saw the devotees of our great lord of fertile Cēṟai in the forest</l>
<l>With flowers bearing bees, this is the way my heart and both my eyes rejoice.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
